EE, Maths PhD 可以入外國大IT公司（Microsoft，Facebook，IBM，etc）做技術性職位。我識有NDS香港畢業PhD畢業後去咗Google總部dup code。"},{"pid":"398205d6ffb3ce6ba9987cc3f2794626a9a6452d","tid":227100,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T03:45:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係咪30歲畢業搵唔到大學工就拜拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇你既值唔值係指邊方面?<br />\n金錢既回報?</blockquote><br />\n如果為咗搵錢邊方面PhD 植得讀</blockquote><br />\nPure maths PhD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲慘過PhD送pizza嗰啲外賣仔，三思</blockquote><br />\n讀數應該好好景架，而且你物理唔差的話<br />\n<br />\n以前呀sir吹棒呢兩科係所有野嘅根本</blockquote><br />\n你阿sir係以唔會齋讀數做前提，佢一早假設咗讀數會再搭少少applications或第二科咁樣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但純數唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n純數可以只為學術而生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n讀完真係可以好窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n純數分別真係好大<br />\n叻嘅話直入名校做asso prof月入&gt;100k HKD<br />\n但係差少少都直接比人淘汰<br />\n消失到無影無蹤</blockquote><br />\n又或者你個field無人care嘅話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e74686bf461e0d0f3865a989f539ec988aa49b46","tid":227100,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T03:55:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Computer Science, EE, Maths PhD 可以入外國大IT公司（Microsoft，Facebook，IBM，etc）做技術性職位。我識有NDS香港畢業PhD畢業後去咗Google總部dup code。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nQuantitative既phd幾時都有transferable skills既優勢，係industry同academia之間彈出彈入都得。<br />\n<br />\n至於去google dup codes，Bachelor都照樣去到既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我有幾個 CU fds bachelor 一grad直去美國google/cisco做<br />\n<br />\n但social sci/pure life sci果班真係食栗米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  BIO友萬年post doc跳唔出個輪迴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cff8a2cd9eae253c0b99b2871d64754eb278dc59","tid":227100,"uid":54733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T03:56:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/d3501404780492z13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fd3501404780492z13.jpg&h=ec51041c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eaeb4675a7baabe8a6814ec925de9b686b116ad5","tid":227100,"uid":49144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T03:56:06.000Z","msg":"PhD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"737ecf4944b4dec10b14277a52b1d0286c902d86","tid":227100,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T04:01:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>隔離個resesrch post 開到 (13)，其中一個永恆話題，就係講緊學術界既job market幾咁扭曲，幾咁剝削。<br />\n<br />\nPhd得兩個情況係值得讀，（1）為左移民/去外國見識下，（2）為左學術。<br />\n<br />\n如果你唔係以上兩點，phd一定唔抵。<br />\n<br />\n特別係搵錢方面，完全冇guarantee<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇返grad schools某d graduate profile，有人讀完phd都淨係做RA</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁為教學唔讀可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n為教學，點解一定要係大學教？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果講教學，我會assume講緊一般港制/美制lecturer，而唔係professorship。<br />\n<br />\n不過大學教書係自由d既，同埋對住班undergraduate起碼似係教緊大人，唔係教細路仔。<br />\n<br />\n如果理想係去大學做lecturer，咁讀phd都正路。不過金錢回報就低過中學老師好多。不過如果係為理想，咁就冇辦法啦。"},{"pid":"8324f92ed1792ef8bcea630e26bae7f8cef1495b","tid":227100,"uid":57675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T04:08:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇你既值唔值係指邊方面?<br />\n金錢既回報?</blockquote><br />\n如果為咗搵錢邊方面PhD 植得讀</blockquote><br />\nPure maths PhD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲慘過PhD送pizza嗰啲外賣仔，三思</blockquote><br />\n讀數應該好好景架，而且你物理唔差的話<br />\n<br />\n以前呀sir吹棒呢兩科係所有野嘅根本</blockquote><br />\n你阿sir係以唔會齋讀數做前提，佢一早假設咗讀數會再搭少少applications或第二科咁樣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但純數唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n純數可以只為學術而生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n讀完真係可以好窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n純數分別真係好大<br />\n叻嘅話直入名校做asso prof月入&gt;100k HKD<br />\n但係差少少都直接比人淘汰<br />\n消失到無影無蹤</blockquote><br />\n又或者你個field無人care嘅話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果勁嘅話都未算太灰嘅<br />\n有啲大學會當集郵咁請埋<br />\n但係出手高唔高就真係唔知"}]}